Distribution. Western Atlantic— USA (Florida), Gulf of Mexico , Mexico , Virgin Islands , Colombia , Venezuela , Trinidad and Tobago , Brazil ( Rio Grande do Norte , Paraíba , Pernambuco , Alagoas , Bahia , Espírito Santo , Rio de Janeiro , São Paulo , Paraná , Santa Catarina); Eastern Pacific— Ecuador , Peru ( Haig 1960 ; Veloso & Melo 1993 ; Coelho-Santos & Coelho 1994 ;
Werding et al. 2003
;
Hiller et al. 2004
;
Rodríguez et al. 2005
;
Coelho et al. 2007
; Ferreira & Melo 2016 ).

Remarks.
This species is found in symbiosis with bryozoan and polychaete species, as well as on rocky shores (

Gore 
et al.
1978

; 
Mantelatto & Souza-Carey 1998
; 
Micheletti-Flores & Negreiros-Fransozo 1999
; 
Hattori & Pinheiro 2001
; 
Bosa & Masunari 2002
; 
Leone & Mantelatto 2015
) and on mussel farming ropes (

Macedo 
et al.
2012

). Sequences accession numbers (GenBank): CCDB 423—16S (
KC858091
), COI (KC85810) (
Leone & Mantelatto 2015
).
